Sobyanin announced the launch of a new generation train “Moscow-2024” on the metro line
Its main differences from the trains of the previous series:
The distance in the aisle has been expanded - the capacity of the car
Show more
increased by 17 people;
The seats have become wider and therefore more comfortable; more practical material has been used for their upholstery;
USB chargers have been moved from the seats to the handrails; plans include installing new Type-C ports and increasing the number of connectors;
The head carriages are equipped for passengers with limited mobility.
The share of modern cars in the Moscow metro has already reached 74%. The renewal of the rolling stock does not stop there - now the development of an even more modern Moscow-2026 train is underway.

Forwarded from: Rogers Kitchen
